snippet.title: The Backrooms: Realism - The Engorger 2
snippet.description:
Didn't know what to call this one. It's just a more up-to-date version than the last one I showed, and I even have early Adrenaline in the game.

It lets you run at Injured Running speed consistently, without worrying about stamina, allowing an easier getaway when injured.
